# Typography Rules

**Display/Headings:**
- Use --font-display (serif or distinctive sans)
- Letter-spacing: -0.03em to -0.05em
- Line-height: 0.9 to 1.1
- Hero size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 5rem)

**Body Text:**
- Use --font-body
- Normal letter-spacing
- Line-height: 1.5 to 1.7
- Size: 1rem to 1.125rem

# Motion & Animation

Every interactive element must have hover/focus states.

**Custom Easing (never use 'ease' or 'linear'):**
--ease-out: cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
--ease-out-back: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
--ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.65, 0, 0.35, 1);

**Transitions:** 200ms var(--ease-out) for interactions

