# Anti-Patterns (NEVER DO)

❌ Purple/blue gradients on white backgrounds
❌ Generic hero sections with centered text
❌ "Get Started" buttons in blue/purple gradient
❌ Perfectly symmetrical layouts
❌ Gray text on white (#6b7280 on #ffffff)
❌ Tailwind's default color palette
❌ Rounded cards with subtle shadows and no personality
❌ Sans-serif everything

# UI Pre-Flight Checklist

Before ANY UI code:
□ Font pairing chosen (not blacklisted)
□ Color palette defined with CSS variables
□ Style recipe selected
□ Design intent confirmed

Before completing ANY component:
□ Hover states on interactive elements
□ Focus states for accessibility
□ Custom easing (not 'ease' or 'linear')
□ Does NOT look like a Tailwind template
